{
  "stem": "26142.12",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jackson.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at this point, he and all of his brothers are still alive, and he has come to Debrecen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in Debrecen, my brother managed to find a-- a place for me that it-- it was a Gentile neighborhood, in a Gentile neighborhood, to rent a place for me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the-- the Jewish neighborhoods were constantly [? razia. ?] The Hungarian [? razia-- ?]",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Raids.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would block up two, three blocks, close them up, and, and, and search all over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and actually what they were doing, they were looking for people like, like us that had no-- had no papers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And in this place here, I managed to get a very good place that was a Gentile neighborhood, and very seldom that they made [? razias ?] in that area.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the owner was a-- the owner of the house was a World War I Hungarian veteran, and an invalid, a hero of World War I.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that plaque was on the, on the door of the gate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And usually, the police or gendarmes or whatever, they wouldn't come in into this place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was hiding out in this-- this place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at that time, at that time already I remember I started to record the, the, the trace back from the days we left Torun to write a diary.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it got lost.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I remember that's what I-- that's what I was doing already then.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 12 SECONDS] It dragged on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It dragged on in Debrecen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was May, 1942.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] We were in Debrecen another-- till October, November.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in Debrecen, I was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my brother [NON-ENGLISH] was in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
